OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776085869
OL,3,CMore rail stations could come to the
OL,4,CMidlands to help communities 'left
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,FMulti-million pound plans to further
OL,8,Fexpand the rail network across the
OL,9,FWest Midlands are under consideration
OL,10,Fby the region's Mayor, ITV News
OL,11,FCentral can reveal.
OL,13,FRichard Parker said his team will be
OL,14,Flooking at business cases for new
OL,15,Fstations to benefit inner city areas
OL,16,Fwhich suffer from highly-congested
OL,17,Froads, poor parking, and aging
OL,18,Finfrastructure.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776085869
OL,3,CMore rail stations could come to the
OL,4,CMidlands to help communities 'left
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,FIt comes in the wake of the Camp Hill
OL,8,Fline opening earlier this week, with
OL,9,Fnew stations now operating from
OL,10,FMoseley Village, Kings Heath, and
OL,11,FPineapple Road.
OL,13,F"I would like to see us investing in
OL,14,Fnew stations, like the three that have
OL,15,Fopened here in south Birmingham over
OL,16,Fthe last two weeks," Mr Parker told
OL,17,FITV News Central.
OL,26,@xD@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776085869
OL,3,CMore rail stations could come to the
OL,4,CMidlands to help communities 'left
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,F"We'll be looking at future cases for
OL,8,Finvesting in more stations, because I
OL,9,Fknow - we all know - the difference
OL,10,Fthey can make, both in terms of
OL,11,Fconnecting people to places where we
OL,12,Fneed to get to, but also regenerating
OL,13,Fthose communities, too.
OL,15,F"We've got #2.5bn of funding from the
OL,16,Fgovernment, and I was really clear
OL,17,Fthat I wanted that funding to benefit
OL,18,Fevery part of the region. That
OL,19,Fincludes - where there is a strong
OL,20,Fbusiness case - investing in new train
OL,21,Fstations too.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
