OL,3,CMore rail stations could come to the
OL,4,CMidlands to help communities 'left
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,F"Residents of Balsall Heath and
OL,8,FSparkbrook are among those to have
OL,9,Fspoken out to make the case for their
OL,10,Fareas to be considered for future
OL,11,Fdevelopments.
OL,13,FThe Camp Hill line passes through
OL,14,FBalsall Heath, across Runcorn Road -
OL,15,Fwhich used to be home to the area's
OL,16,Fformer station, which shut down during
OL,17,Fthe Second World War.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
