OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776085869
OL,3,CMore rail stations could come to the
OL,4,CMidlands to help communities 'left
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,F"It's one of Birmingham's most
OL,8,Fdeprived areas. So just knowing that
OL,9,Fthere was care and love and that we
OL,10,Fwere involved in this South Birmingham
OL,11,Frailway station project, along with
OL,12,Fthe history that we've got here in
OL,13,FBalsall Heath - I think that would
OL,14,Freally increase pride, bring jobs to
OL,15,Fthe area, and give people more freedom
OL,16,Fof movement around."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
