PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776085869
OL,3,CMore rail stations could come to the
OL,4,CMidlands to help communities 'left
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,FThere are no formal proposals for any
OL,8,Fnew stations at this stage, but the
OL,9,Fgovernment awarded the #2.5bn, four-
OL,10,Fyear funding plan to West Midlands
OL,11,FCombined Authority last year, with the
OL,12,Faim of allowing the Mayor to push
OL,13,Fforward with plans he says will boost
OL,14,Fthe economy and improve the lives of
OL,15,Fpeople across the region.
OL,17,FMr Parker said he was determined not
OL,18,Fto "repeat the mistakes of the past",
OL,19,Fwith the three newly-opened stations
OL,20,Fbeing finished years, and tens of
OL,21,Fmillions of pounds, above expectations.
OL,26,@zD@DOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1776085869
OL,3,CMore rail stations could come to the
OL,4,CMidlands to help communities 'left
OL,5,Cbehind'
OL,7,F"We're putting teams in place to make
OL,8,Fsure all future capital projects are
OL,9,Fproperly planned, properly designed
OL,10,Fand costed and also they're going to
OL,11,Fbe delivered on time," he added.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow..
